      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DOONGALLA SERENA (3) lines up chasing three wins on end after scoring over 500m at this track in 28.18 last time, set up by a fast early sectional. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Great chance to get the job done again. DURAN OLLY (8) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Grade 5 at Sandown. Key player on best and worth another try. SERRATED EDGE (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind DOONGALLA SERENA (28.46) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Will give a great sight again.",
